    • UpdateMessage

      public UpdateMessage​(int playerId, int playerPos, int nextPlayerId, Resource[][] marketBoard, Resource extraMarble, java.util.List<java.lang.Integer> availableProductionCards, java.util.List<BiElement<java.lang.Integer,​java.lang.Integer>> productionCardsId, java.util.List<BiElement<java.lang.Integer,​java.lang.Boolean>> leadersId, java.util.Map<BiElement<Resource,​Storage>,​java.lang.Integer> addedResources, java.util.Map<BiElement<Resource,​Storage>,​java.lang.Integer> removedResources)
      Parameters:
      playerId - is the player that has caused changes in the model
      playerPos - how far the player that caused this update message is gone on the faith track
      nextPlayerId - is the next player that has to play the turn
      marketBoard - the new market configuration
      extraMarble - the new extra marble in market
      availableProductionCards - the 12 production cards available for purchase, after the player (playerId has made some changes
      productionCardsId - production card's id bought by the playerId (T) player and the stack where it's been put (V)
      leadersId - active leaders that playerId has
      addedResources - all the resources that playerId has (lootchest, warehouse, extraStorage) in that moment
      removedResources - all the resources removed from playerId's storage (lootchest, warehouse, extraStorage) once the turn was over
